  "name": "SimpleWhite about:newtab Tiles Fix",
  "description": "This gives the option to remove the perspective (oblique/slant appearance) form the tiles in the new tab page when using <i>Louis Chan</i>'s <a href=https://www.louis.hk/whitefox/><i><b>Simple White</b></i></a> theme (or its variations) in <b>Firefox</b>.  It also gives the a choice to display smaller tiles in that page.  You can select from a list of progressively smaller tiles sizes with different aspect ratios.",
